;How to toggle the Sidebar display using a button?
Use the `action-setfield` widget and change the text value of `$:/state/sidebar` as below

* `no`: hide the Sidebar
* `yes`: show the Sidebar

<$macrocall $name="wikitext-example-without-html" 
src="""<$button>
<$action-setfield $tiddler="$:/state/sidebar" text ="no"/>
Hide Sidebar
</$button>
<$button>
<$action-setfield $tiddler="$:/state/sidebar" text ="yes"/>
Show Sidebar
</$button>
"""/>

